## 📋 Common PropTypes Validators

| Validator | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| `PropTypes.string` | Must be a string |
| `PropTypes.number` | Must be a number |
| `PropTypes.bool` | Must be true/false |
| `PropTypes.func` | Must be a function |
| `PropTypes.array` | Must be an array |
| `PropTypes.object` | Must be an object |
| `PropTypes.node` | Anything renderable (string, number, element, fragment) |
| `PropTypes.element` | A React element |
| `PropTypes.oneOf([...])` | Enum-like restriction to specific values |
| `PropTypes.shape({...})` | Object with a specific shape |
| `PropTypes.arrayOf(type)` | Array of a certain type |
| `PropTypes.instanceOf(Class)` | Instance of a specific class |

